Class TrieNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.dpark20.trie.TrieNode

  • public class TrieNode
extends Object
    Class for Nodes of our Trie, keeping track of one letter within node, and references to all relevant info (full word, counts, etc.).
